{"id": 2821, "genre": 1001, "title": "这些年，你都把哪些锅甩给了“手机”？", "description": "说不清是因为拖延症才刷手机，还是有了手机之后才变拖延了，先怪手机再说。（题图来自：iStock ©️roberuto）", "record_count": 2278, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190304174746lKuXUtJmzS4nHDj1.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-11T03:00:14Z", "options": [{"id": 332297, "content": "模糊了工作与生活的界限，回家了还得随时工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 250, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131155}, {"id": 332298, "content": "不想找女朋友就是手机看pornhub挺方便的，电脑也是（；￣ェ￣）", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307872}, {"id": 332299, "content": "好奇心日报太好看了，我都没时间干别的了😏", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603670}, {"id": 332300, "content": "懒惰、拖延症", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 332301, "content": "毁掉一个孩子最简单的方法就是给他一部手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135562}, {"id": 332302, "content": "没有写完作业是因为被手机的推送吸引了", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606223}, {"id": 332303, "content": "学习不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583850}, {"id": 334095, "content": "手机太复杂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572249}, {"id": 332304, "content": "学习不好，", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1547567}, {"id": 332305, "content": "懒的去社交", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606224}, {"id": 332561, "content": "没甩锅给手机。只不过更多时候手机变成了我们的透气孔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269442}, {"id": 332306, "content": "静不下来  没空思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 143, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 332307, "content": "赖床", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449032}, {"id": 332308, "content": "吃饭，学习，睡觉之前都想玩一会儿手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386926}, {"id": 332311, "content": "不要熬夜，熬夜对手机不好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253166}, {"id": 332312, "content": "让我混日子", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208674}, {"id": 339224, "content": "手机让我负面情绪更严重，让我看待世人的眼光发生了变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637638}, {"id": 332313, "content": "视力下降", "image": null, "praise_count": 225, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 332314, "content": "三心二意", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1594648}, {"id": 332315, "content": "没有女朋友，都怪手机太好玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713195}, {"id": 332317, "content": "不去参加聚会，因为手机没电了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525474}, {"id": 332829, "content": "屏幕不够大，看视频眼睛酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544180}, {"id": 333597, "content": "复习集中不了精力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607837}, {"id": 332318, "content": "今天天气不太好，都怪手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020655}, {"id": 332319, "content": "还是会让人熬夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606281}, {"id": 332320, "content": "摆脱无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606279}, {"id": 336160, "content": "视力下降，颈椎不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619261}, {"id": 332321, "content": "什么都可以离开，就是离不开手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606013}, {"id": 332322, "content": "手机太滑了，老是摔", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555854}, {"id": 332323, "content": "社恐：看到微信消息就头疼\n焦虑：