, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343837}, {"id": 332342, "content": "要用手机干正事，查资料，之后拿起手机不知不觉点了别的看了好久，看的都忘了自己最初想要干什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606378}, {"id": 332343, "content": "颈椎病，腕管综合征，近视，强迫症", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590523}, {"id": 332600, "content": "分手快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431366}, {"id": 333625, "content": "既然是甩锅 那就甩的干净点  都怪手机 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857352}, {"id": 332350, "content": "没有手机可以干太多事，有了手机就啥啥都忘了干", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606406}]}